                                  <span>Would raising the minimum wage to $15 improve the US economy?</span><br>
                              </div>
                              <div class="item">
                                  <span>Is the affordable care act harmful to small businesses?</span><br>
                              </div>
                              <div class="item">
                                  <span>Can gun safety legislation reduce the likelihood of the next mass shooting?</span><br>
                              </div>
                              <div class="item">
                                  <span> Is the NAFTA free trade agreement been harmful to the US employment?</span><br>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </h2>
                        <div class="hero-image">
                            <img src="assets/charity_debate_header2.svg" alt="matchup" class="img-responsive charity_header">
                        </div>
                        <h1 class="intro-tagline"> They debate. You Decide. $25,000 to the winner's charity.</h1>
